{"tid":2334146,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"星島社論沒告訴你的事 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-12-21T03:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T05:25:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"087419fd9e5e30ddb8fcbb61b38f54fd09bc2113","tid":2334146,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:29:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201221/DQT63GFLQJEMZMZ26S5V64T3SA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201221%2FDQT63GFLQJEMZMZ26S5V64T3SA%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzPvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=55e51eeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201221%2FDQT63GFLQJEMZMZ26S5V64T3SA%2F&h=c2ef05a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201221/DQT63GFLQJEMZMZ26S5V64T3SA/</a><br />\n<br />\n星島社論沒告訴你的事 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LXLYMJcN_rd--qLk8mcCv3vJGt8=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N7QHCNJKSVHBXALRLR2IQVZGYQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLXLYMJcN_rd--qLk8mcCv3vJGt8%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN7QHCNJKSVHBXALRLR2IQVZGYQ.png&h=cc567e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本欄讀者應該知道，儘管我常常批評所謂行政長官，但我的批評完全基於事實，且動機極度良善&mdash;&mdash;我只望特首三省其身，覺今是而昨非，改善特區政府施政而已。因此，林鄭上任三年以來，我非但從未叫她下台，反而屢次勉勵她繼續做特首，最好做到氣絕身亡。如果塵世間真有「忠誠反對派」，就是我了。<br />\n<br />\n反觀近日特區土共，無理刁難習近平的愛將林鄭月娥，打狗不看主人面，不知有何居心。何以說他們「無理刁難」呢？我用例子答你。全國政協常委何柱國旗下的《星島日報》，十二月十七日社論說：「內地以全民檢測遏止疫情，成果舉世公認，從科學角度評估也得到證明，例如早前青島市出現確診，全市於五天內為近一千萬居民進行核酸檢測，找到播毒者即隔離，經此『閃電包圍戰』，市內再無病例。」大家看到問題嗎？<br />\n<br />\n《星島》社論大力吹捧的「青島模式」，實情是這樣的：青島市在十月十一日發現三名無症狀感染者後，連夜啟動全民檢測，五天內完成全市過千萬人採驗。為什麼這樣神速？《星島》沒告訴你，原來青島政府運用了最尖端的「10合1混採檢測技術」，即是將十人的採驗樣本，集合於一支採集管測試，原理就像一個屎坑十個人一齊蹲，屎坑效率也自然高上十倍。<br />\n<br />\n然而「青島模式」最震驚七十億人，不&mdash;&mdash;國內十四億同胞該不會震驚&mdash;&mdash;<span class=\"orange\">最震驚全球五十六億人的事實是：青島五日內完成的1089萬9145份檢測，結果是：全，部，陰，性！</span>換言之，無人需要隔離。須知每個檢驗方式都有某比例的誤差，總會出現偽陰性或偽陽性，但現在一千萬次檢測居然全體陰性，這簡直是超自然現象。<br />\n<br />\n既然說內地全民檢測「成果舉世公認」，國家這次創造超自然奇蹟，為什麼《星島》社論非但沒熱烈頌讚，反而含糊其辭隻字不提，是否別有用心？如果發起「批林運動」的土共，跟《星島》社論一樣，主張香港全民檢測以「十合一」青島模式進行，請他們光明磊落說出來。你要嘅話，就講吖嘛；你唔講，林鄭同市民又點知你要呢？你話你係咪無理刁難？"},{"pid":"6e54b25eb261cca1a3a767dc0a023ba0115c3729","tid":2334146,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:34:08.000Z","msg":"青島單野我懷疑冇驗過, 所以十合一無所謂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221140a6cecb77f70910fb3142171997ea958e01","tid":2334146,"uid":38633,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"087419fd9e5e30ddb8fcbb61b38f54fd09bc2113","tid":2334146,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:29:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201221/DQT63GFLQJEMZMZ26S5V64T3SA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201221%2FDQT63GFLQJEMZMZ26S5V64T3SA%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzPvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=55e51eeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201221%2FDQT63GFLQJEMZMZ26S5V64T3SA%2F&h=c2ef05a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201221/DQT63GFLQJEMZMZ26S5V64T3SA/</a><br />\n<br />\n星島社論沒告訴你的事 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LXLYMJcN_rd--qLk8mcCv3vJGt8=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N7QHCNJKSVHBXALRLR2IQVZGYQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLXLYMJcN_rd--qLk8mcCv3vJGt8%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN7QHCNJKSVHBXALRLR2IQVZGYQ.png&h=cc567e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本欄讀者應該知道，儘管我常常批評所謂行政長官，但